{"tid":573631,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"狗年第三擊：中鐵建","createTime":"2018-02-26T15:33:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-26T18:12:04.000Z","uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"5abc92be8f8b523bdfb21c2e33cd8b5645d7d51f","tid":573631,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T15:33:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180225/large/1519540030_9788.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180225%2Flarge%2F1519540030_9788.jpg&h=2dc02f03&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今日推介狗年第三擊：中鐵建（1186）。去年，H指大升36%，中鐵建則跌9%，今年H指升9%，中䥫建仍跌6%，現價8.51元，只較52周低位微高5%。中鐵建被剔出H指成份股，沒有什麼大不了，正好趁殘價上車。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180225/large/1519555284_3787.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180225%2Flarge%2F1519555284_3787.jpg&h=ccb79394&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1）中鐵建丶中交建（1800）與中鐵（390），是3大主流鐵路基建股，相關股有中車（1766）及中車時代（3898）。5隻股票通常獲市場視為「同一堆」而作比較，原本全是H指成分股。中鐵建市值較中交建及中鐵為小（其實不小，A＋H總值1,689億元），遭剔出H指，相信只是因為同類股太多，要騰空1個位予新進者，而與基本因素無關。事實上，中鐵建業績勝同業平均。<br />\n追失地 博翻半番<br />\n<br />\n2）去年首3季，中鐵建純利105.25億元人幣，按年增長15%；中交建與中鐵同期平均多賺12%，中車及中車時代平均少賺12%。彭博綜合券商預測，中鐵建2018年PE僅5.3倍，殘爆，較8年平均9.7倍折讓4成半。中交建與中鐵平均6.1倍，亦屬不貴，中車及中車時代平均12.4倍。<br />\n<br />\n3）中鐵建2018年預期PB僅0.58倍，較8年平均1.1倍折讓近一半。中交建及中跌平均亦只是0.6倍，中車及中車時代平均則高達1.66倍。<br />\n<br />\n＊中鐵建有望追回過去年幾的失地，目標價12.8元，潛在升幅50%；目標價PE不過8倍，仍較過去平均打了8折。亦可按比例套裝買入，每買4注中鐵建，中交建及中鐵各下1 注。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>中石油點解睇7蚊</strong><br />\n<br />\n同場加映：從PB着眼，中石油(857)令人心動。英美油股BP丶殼牌丶埃克森丶雪佛龍等，今年平均PB1.47倍，中海油（883）與中石化386)平均0.95倍。中石油今年預期PB只有0.69倍，較同業大折讓，亦遠低於8年平均的1.17倍。<br />\n<br />\n中石油現價5.57元，較上月杪6.66元低16%，而油價同期只低4%，中石油跌過度。博油價收復4%的失地，及中石油不合理的低PB稍為向上修正，目標價可設於7元，即上月高位加5%，潛在升幅26%，折合PB不過0.87倍，只是英美同業的6折以下。<br />\n<br />\n何車<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180225/57873487\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180225%2F57873487&d=TDtlRchWnweuUVE0faERTS7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=24afa5b7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180225%2F57873487&h=0bb7add8\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180225/57873487</a>"},{"pid":"c427dcb3028d4d8c7bbd4f5b6895bd1efd531781","tid":573631,"uid":109386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T15:40:17.000Z","msg":"個人認為中交建著數d，富者越富，一帶一路都係交建行先"},{"pid":"3da045515f6a2fb65e1432fe0f0c5821624a2f59","tid":573631,"uid":28163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T15:42:52.000Z","msg":"隻野個沽空咁大既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"537c3d1d5f725836821d31455dd6f8bcfb1b40f3","tid":573631,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T15:47:35.000Z","msg":"中國的鐵路股票我一向唔敢掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"251b1b1c5b77f77d546c0e6ef5cd12c4cbdaac2e","tid":573631,"uid":5278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"537c3d1d5f725836821d31455dd6f8bcfb1b40f3","tid":573631,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T15:47:35.000Z","msg":"中國的鐵路股票我一向唔敢掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T15:54:13.000Z","msg":"掂親都輸錢 不了"},{"pid":"79a39c52d71b255aa4e5de74f90a24d3aa9b6ee8","tid":573631,"uid":42473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T15:56:34.000Z","msg":"強者越強 弱者就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dde27f58aa470b15c46b4cb5713ebe44b533c9be","tid":573631,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"537c3d1d5f725836821d31455dd6f8bcfb1b40f3","tid":573631,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T15:47:35.000Z","msg":"中國的鐵路股票我一向唔敢掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T16:02:55.000Z","msg":"隱藏的債一定很多<br />\n否則解釋唔到成個版塊都殘"},{"pid":"d869f93c4d3c87f77d27d5ca8ab903110c972515","tid":573631,"uid":172513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T16:10:32.000Z","msg":"真係不要亂掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n高鐵已經話左俾人聽，真係有蝕無賺。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e920d6069ec48f5666d17fb2935f593832e1ff6b","tid":573631,"uid":98784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T16:12:52.000Z","msg":"何車條仆街仲未死？"},{"pid":"c574491bf3759d77e3f45976e8b201737f11a2ec","tid":573631,"uid":36390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T16:49:16.000Z","msg":"借債度日的公司"},{"pid":"43462192824d0899ce4cb391ab2eef8360b21689","tid":573631,"uid":71748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T16:52:35.000Z","msg":"如果唔找數比佢都唔知點算"},{"pid":"0f011f6d58455c494755e159844bc93928510dab","tid":573631,"uid":103451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T18:12:04.000Z","msg":"十七歲買入中鐵建，A股我挑戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}